name: G E N E S I S
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #001]

G E N E S I S

A prophetic sigil of new tidings. It stands for when a large scale transmutation process begins. An egg crack might be heralded as the savior or as the downfall. Or it might go unnoticed entirely.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
